{"tid":989919,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"尼馬：世界盃我無插水","createTime":"2019-01-21T08:13:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T08:23:24.000Z","uid":94771,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"683b779c5799a75547584f3eb0df5bfb82d564ce","tid":989919,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T08:13:10.000Z","msg":"Goal報導，最近比利批評尼馬：要多入球少插水。對此尼馬表示，他尊重但並不認同。<br />\n<br />\n　　尼馬說：「<span style=\"color: red;\">比利的批評？我覺得很有趣。只要你不贏波，就會有批評聲到來。在世界盃期間，我從來沒有插水過，都是被對手犯規</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「如今大家非常熱衷於討論這件事，<span style=\"color: red;\">因為那是尼馬，一切都被放大了</span>。我尊重比利的批評，但是我並不認同。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「我要離開的謠言？自從我成為一名職業球員，就一直有謠言。但是現在並沒有任何具體的事情發生。一旦確定了，我會公開談的。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「我想贏得一切，特別是歐聯，因為它是每一球員的夢想。我們需要在歐聯中成長，大家在攻防兩端都要做得很好。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V9S5w2uaMok\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DV9S5w2uaMok&d=w7%2FbDBVMSsXhjs7ptAmemFzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=37c4e5f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=V9S5w2uaMok</a><br />\n<br />\n邊有放大到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"900198a2aa8beaa31ad934123ddb8ba4d2692c5a","tid":989919,"uid":555,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T08:15:42.000Z","msg":"掂唔到就話插水啫 被人踢到都叫插水？"},{"pid":"5eb740fdaf1e3b4fd8b01a557832d9785d5e530a","tid":989919,"uid":58811,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T08:18:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2n6p2y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2n6p2y.png&h=abfc0ec0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3362a6e7792a790c4619fcdad64a0e4225f5d4a6","tid":989919,"uid":5190,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T08:18:54.000Z","msg":"認同尼馬 佢每次都係俾人針對"},{"pid":"35c4339aa6e81e83dab0d1a1ca76ad74aadee18b","tid":989919,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5eb740fdaf1e3b4fd8b01a557832d9785d5e530a","tid"